full_description:
PC Power VT-S200B PLUS 230W Power Supply

The PC Power VT-S200B PLUS 230W Power Supply is a reliable choice for an efficient power supply in your computer system. This power supply, with a maximum power output of 230 watts, offers reliable and constant power to your components, allowing your system to run smoothly. This power supply maintains excellent cooling, providing effective heat dissipation throughout the operation, due to its 120mm fan with ball bearing technology. The dependable design of the fan helps extend the power supply's lifetime, increasing its durability for long-term operation. The PC Power VT-S200B PLUS has an ATX form factor and is hence compatible with a broad range of computer chassis. It has key connections, such as three SATA connectors and one IDE connector, for attaching storage devices and other peripherals. The power supply has two four-pin peripheral connections, which improves its compatibility with diverse components. This power supply is non-modular, which ensures simplicity and ease of use. Because of its non-modular design, all wires are permanently linked, removing the burden of handling various cords and ensuring a nice and ordered interior for your PC. The PC Power VT-S200B PLUS 230W Power Supply is an excellent alternative for those looking for a solid power solution for their desktop PCs. It is reliable, effective, and simple to install.
